cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.PL, cs.CC 

This paper deals with formal logic and reasoning, specifically in the context of knowledge and time. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also involves agents and their knowledge, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also discusses semantic properties of agents, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
